":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"要睇匹數同你間屋大細, 不過都無可能0.2-0.3KW 咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkelectric.com/en/customer-services/billing-payment-electricity-tariffs/know-more-about-electricity-consumption/estimated-electricity-cost-of-common-appliances\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkelectric.com%2Fen%2Fcustomer-services%2Fbilling-payment-electricity-tariffs%2Fknow-more-about-electricity-consumption%2Festimated-electricity-cost-of-common-appliances&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=63611bd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkelectric.com/en/customer-services/billing-payment-electricity-tariffs/know-more-about-electricity-consumption/estimated-electricity-cost-of-common-appliances</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T09:36:29.000Z","msg":"溫度的高低固然會影響用電量的多寡，濕度同樣有相當大的影響力。電器如電暖爐及冷氣機同樣耗電。例如：<strong>一部2000w 的電暖爐運作一小時，耗電量大約為<span class=\"red\">2度，相等於一部2匹冷氣機一小時的耗電量</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>即使是抽濕機，一部抽水量達24公升的抽濕機，運作一小時的耗電量大約為0.3度，相等於一部0.75匹冷氣機<span class=\"red\">半小時的耗電量</span>。</strong>隨著氣?的變化，一些電器用品的耗電量也受影響，例如：雪櫃、冷氣機及電暖爐等。<br />\n<br />\n搵埋中電:<br />\n0.75匹都 0.6度 wor<br />\n2匹就2度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.clp.com.hk/zh/customer-service/frequency-asked-questions/high-consumption-factors#T2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clp.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fcustomer-service%2Ffrequency-asked-questions%2Fhigh-consumption-factors%23T2&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=625726c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clp.com.hk/zh/customer-service/frequency-asked-questions/high-consumption-factors#T2</a>"},{"pid":"47d456a5f63e9b820192cc007bfb9ad4dc47bddc","tid":2280040,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"3個月$1200即係1個月$400，夏天黎計唔算太多<br />\n我一條友夏天日均用電最多10度，冬天4度<br />\n月均電費應該$150-$350左右？（近排好多個月都唔洗交電費，實數幾多冇上心）<br />\n正常夏天一日開8-12個鐘冷氣<br />\n2xx升3門雪櫃，5x吋電視，全屋led燈，久唔久用電磁爐/空氣炸煱煮下飯，冬天打下邊爐咁"},{"pid":"e286b9df7c5472a52715923bfd7f77e47e320cc1","tid":2280040,"uid":363579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d456a5f63e9b820192cc007bfb9ad4dc47bddc","tid":2280040,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"3個月$1200即係1個月$400，夏天黎計唔算太多<br />\n我一條友夏天日均用電最多10度，冬天4度<br />\n月均電費應該$150-$350左右？（近排好多個月都唔洗交電費，實數幾多冇上心）<br />\n正常夏天一日開8-12個鐘冷氣<br />\n2xx升3門雪櫃，5x吋電視，全屋led燈，久唔久用電磁爐/空氣炸煱煮下飯，冬天打下邊爐咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"醒起屋企用電磁爐，都可能係原因<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170810845bf36c29e30041aea3d29a8d73fa1e6b","tid":2280040,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e286b9df7c5472a52715923bfd7f77e47e320cc1","tid":2280040,"uid":363579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47d456a5f63e9b820192cc007bfb9ad4dc47bddc","tid":2280040,"uid":249252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"3個月$1200即係1個月$400，夏天黎計唔算太多<br />\n我一條友夏天日均用電最多10度，冬天4度<br />\n月均電費應該$150-$350左右？（近排好多個月都唔洗交電費，實數幾多冇上心）<br />\n正常夏天一日開8-12個鐘冷氣<br />\n2xx升3門雪櫃，5x吋電視，全屋led燈，久唔久用電磁爐/空氣炸煱煮下飯，冬天打下邊爐咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:17:52.000Z","msg":"醒起屋企用電磁爐，都可能係原因<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"電磁爐正常煮一個人份量2至3餸開30鐘1000w計都係0.5度電，比起冷氣其實有限數"}]}